Resource Profile: openIMIS Claim Response

Official URL: https://github.com/openimis/openimis_fhir_r5_ig/StructureDefinition/openimis-claim-response Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2025-08-26 Computable Name: OpenIMISClaimResponse

Defines a ClaimResponse for openIMIS which maps to a Claim. The ClaimResponse resource contains the adjudication result of a Claim.

Usages:

  • Examples for this Profile: ClaimResponse/Claim001
  • CapabilityStatements using this Profile: openIMIS Capability Statement

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
